      • getDependencies

        public java.util.ArrayList<Definition> getDependencies()
        List of all the types and functions that must be defined/declared before this one.

        It includes the types of all the fields, return types of the functions and dependencies of nested types. When the type is not a struct or class it has only one or zero dependencies.

        Specified by:
        getDependencies in interface Definition
        Returns:
        List of all the types and functions.
